flowchart LR
    RCTX[RC Transmitter] -->|2.4 GHz RF| RCRX[RC Receiver\nPWM/SBUS]
    RCRX --> FC

    XP[X-Plane] -->|pppd| FC[Flight Controller]
    FC -->|USB serial| MAVP[MAVProxy]
    MAVP -->|MAVLink UDP| QGC[QGroundControl]
    MAVP -->|MAVLink UDP| SK

    CAM[Kamera] -->|frame| SK[Seeker\ndeteksi / lacak]
    SK -->|error xy| PRED[Prediktor\nLatensi]
    PRED --> SM[State Machine]

    FC -->|telemetri| SM
    SM -->|mode / tracking cmd| FC

    FC -->|telemetri| TEL[Telemetri]
    TEL --> HUD[HudDisplay]
    TEL --> CSV[Logger CSV]
    SM --> HUD
    SM --> CSV

